(79, 'widget_text', 'a:4:{i:2;a:4:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:61:\"Copyright © 2018. The Outlets at Lipa.\r\nAll Rights Reserved.\";s:6:\"filter\";b:1;s:6:\"visual\";b:1;}i:3;a:4:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:212:\"<a href=\"#aboitizNote\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-42\" src=\"http://beta.theloop.ph/theoutletslipa/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/footer-logo.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"95\" /></a>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:1;s:6:\"visual\";b:1;}i:4;a:4:{s:5:\"title\";s:11:\"AboitizLand\";s:4:\"text\";s:816:\"We Are  <img class=\"wp-image-323 alignnone\" src=\"http://beta.theloop.ph/theoutletslipa/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/footer-logo-description.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"153\" height=\"29\" style=\"vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block;\"/>\r\n\r\nAboitizLand, Inc. is the real estate arm of the Aboitiz Group - one of the country’s most successful and respected corporations. It was founded in 1920 and engaged in power distribution and generation, infrastructure, banking, food production, ship building, real estate development, and construction.\r\n\r\nHaving nurtured Cebu’s residential, industrial, and commercial communities with pioneering concepts and ambitious development undertakings, AboitizLand has now ventured to other key cities with quality communities that provide better ways to live for the modern Filipino.\";s:6:\"filter\";b:1;s:6:\"visual\";b:1;}s:12:\"_multiwidget\";i:1;}', 'yes'),
