(3241, 251, 'details_0_content', '<p id=\"E993\"><span id=\"E994\">The Outlets at </span><span id=\"E996\">Lipa</span><span id=\"E998\"> can be accessed through several exits along the South Luzon Expressway (SLEX).</span></p>\r\n<span id=\"E998\"> * </span><span id=\"E1000\">Malvar</span><span id=\"E1002\"> </span>\r\n\r\n<span id=\"E1002\">* </span><span id=\"E1004\">Lipa</span>\r\n\r\n<span id=\"E1006\"> * </span><span id=\"E1008\">Balete</span><span id=\"E1010\"> </span>\r\n<p id=\"E1012\"><span id=\"E1013\">Travel time from key destinations: 1 hour and 16 mins from Makati (approx. 69 km) 1 hour from </span><span id=\"E1015\">Alabang</span><span id=\"E1017\"> (approx. 53 km) </span></p>\r\n<p id=\"E1021\"><span id=\"E1022\">1. Take the </span><span id=\"E1024\">Malvar</span><span id=\"E1026\"> Exit from SLEX. </span></p>\r\n<p id=\"E1027\"><span id=\"E1028\">2. Turn left upon exiting the toll plaza. </span></p>\r\n<p id=\"E1029\"><span id=\"E1030\">3. Turn right along JP Laurel Highway, Lima Technology Center (where The Outlets at </span><span id=\"E1032\">Lipa</span><span id=\"E1034\"> can be found) is straight ahead about 5.5km. Lima Technology Center (LTC) is on your left side. </span></p>\r\n<p id=\"E1035\"><span id=\"E1036\">4. Enter LTC and went straight ahead. The Outlets at </span><span id=\"E1038\">Lipa</span><span id=\"E1040\"> is on the right side of the road coming from the main entrance. </span></p>'),
(3242, 251, '_details_0_content', 'field_5b3bedcf06fc1'),
(3243, 251, 'details_1_title', 'Via Public Transportation'),
(3244, 251, '_details_1_title', 'field_5b3bedcc06fc0'),
(3245, 251, 'details_1_content', '<p id=\"E1044\"><span id=\"E1045\">1. Take a bus going to </span><span id=\"E1047\">Lipa</span><span id=\"E1049\">, </span><span id=\"E1051\">Batangas</span><span id=\"E1053\"> (JAM and Alps Terminals at </span><span id=\"E1055\">Buendia</span><span id=\"E1057\"> and </span><span id=\"E1059\">Cubao</span><span id=\"E1061\">) </span></p>\r\n<p id=\"E1062\"><span id=\"E1063\">2. Ask to be dropped off at </span><span id=\"E1065\">Lipa</span><span id=\"E1067\"> Bus Terminal located at SM </span><span id=\"E1069\">Lipa</span><span id=\"E1071\">. </span></p>\r\n<p id=\"E1072\"><span id=\"E1073\">3. Take a </span><span id=\"E1075\">jeepney</span><span id=\"E1077\"> heading to </span><span id=\"E1079\">Tanauan</span><span id=\"E1081\">. </span></p>\r\n<p id=\"E1082\"><span id=\"E1083\">4. Drop at Lima Technology Center (LTC) main entrance which can be found on your right side. </span></p>\r\n<p id=\"E1084\"><span id=\"E1085\">5. Take a short walk from the LTC main entrance to The Outlets at </span><span id=\"E1087\">Lipa</span><span id=\"E1089\">. </span></p>'),
