(4626, 344, 'details_0_content', '<p id=\"E993\"><span id=\"E994\">The Outlets at </span><span id=\"E996\">Lipa</span><span id=\"E998\"> can be accessed through several exits along the South Luzon Expressway (SLEX).</span></p>\r\n<span id=\"E998\"> * </span><span id=\"E1000\">Malvar</span><span id=\"E1002\"> </span>\r\n\r\n<span id=\"E1002\">* </span><span id=\"E1004\">Lipa</span>\r\n\r\n<span id=\"E1006\"> * </span><span id=\"E1008\">Balete</span><span id=\"E1010\"> </span>\r\n<p id=\"E1012\"><span id=\"E1013\">Travel time from key destinations: 1 hour and 16 mins from Makati (approx. 69 km) 1 hour from </span><span id=\"E1015\">Alabang</span><span id=\"E1017\"> (approx. 53 km) </span></p>\r\n<p id=\"E1021\"><span id=\"E1022\">1. Take the </span><span id=\"E1024\">Malvar</span><span id=\"E1026\"> Exit from SLEX. </span></p>\r\n<p id=\"E1027\"><span id=\"E1028\">2. Turn left upon exiting the toll plaza. </span></p>\r\n<p id=\"E1029\"><span id=\"E1030\">3. Turn right along JP Laurel Highway, Lima Technology Center (where The Outlets at </span><span id=\"E1032\">Lipa</span><span id=\"E1034\"> can be found) is straight ahead about 5.5km. Lima Technology Center (LTC) is on your left side. </span></p>\r\n<p id=\"E1035\"><span id=\"E1036\">4. Enter LTC and went straight ahead. The Outlets at </span><span id=\"E1038\">Lipa</span><span id=\"E1040\"> is on the right side of the road coming from the main entrance. </span></p>'),
(4627, 344, '_details_0_content', 'field_5b3bedcf06fc1'),
