(4629, 344, '_details_2_0_title', 'field_5b3bedde06fc3'),
(4630, 344, 'details_2_0_content', 'Via SLEX The Outlets at Lipa can be accessed through several exits along the South Luzon Expressway (SLEX): * Malvar * Lipa * Balete\r\n\r\nTravel time from key destinations: 1 hour and 16 mins from Makati (approx. 69 km) 1 hour from Alabang (approx. 53 km)\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Take the Malvar Exit from SLEX.</li>\r\n 	<li>Turn left upon exiting the toll plaza.</li>\r\n 	<li>Turn right along JP Laurel Highway, Lima Technology Center (where The Outlets at Lipa can be found) is straight ahead about 5.5km. Lima Technology Center (LTC) is on your left side.</li>\r\n 	<li>Enter LTC and went straight ahead. The Outlets at Lipa is on the right side of the road coming from the main entrance.</li>\r\n</ol>'),
