(31, 1, '2018-07-01 10:32:04', '2018-07-01 10:32:04', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What if you can live your life never settling for anything less than everything? What if you could squeeze every drop; savor every bite, enjoy every second, groove to every beat, give it your all and get it all back in return?</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This philosophy is at the very heart of The Outlets at Lipa, the 9.3 hectare commercial, lifestyle and leisure destination created by AboitizLand Inc., the real estate arm of the Aboitiz Group of Companies.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Whether it be outlet shopping, dining, entertainment, or outdoor activities, The Outlets at Lipa promises to provide the all-out enjoyment every family wants and deserves.</span>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ALL-ACCESS LOCATION</span></i>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Outlets at Lipa is strategically located at the entrance to the LIMA Technolgy Center along the national road of Lipa City. The city itself is the gateway to the Southern Tagalog Region and is easily accessible via an extensive network of highways reaching all the way to Makati in Metro Manila. And of the 2.7 million Batangueños, over 500,000 of them live within 10 kilometers of The Outlets at Lipa.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Batangas province also has one of the Philippines’ fastest growing economies. And its residents are eager reap the rewards of their hard work and get the most out of life – something which they are sure to experience at The Outlets at Lipa.</span>', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2018-07-19 14:44:38', '2018-07-19 14:44:38', '', 0, 'http://beta.theloop.ph/theoutletslipa/?page_id=31', 0, 'page', '', 0),
