(246, 1, '2018-07-17 03:51:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '<div class=\"_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa\">Considered to be the largest artificial turf in Luzon, Aboitiz Pitch opened last June 23 and will complement global and local brands coming to The Outlets at Lipa.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div class=\"_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa\">With a one-day football festival of top Batangas football clubs on its Live All Out event, Aboitiz Pitch launched as an outdoor multi-purpose sports field guaranteeing action-packed activities. It has an open-air layout for a relaxed atmosphere that goes with grand stand and amenities. Various sports can be played including Ultimate Frisbee, Flag football, Dodgeball and Football.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div class=\"_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa\">Complementing the multi-sports field, The Outlets at Lipa will also carry outstanding variety of premium lifestyle brands including H&amp;M, Oakley, Reef, and Dickies, among others, offering discount shopping 365 days of the year.</div>\r\n<div class=\"_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa\">More so, The Outlets will also bring several house of brands such as 158 Designer\'s Boulevard, Bambu, Sunglass Haven, Super Shopbox, Optique Outlet, Sports Warehouse, and US Department Store. Sports brands such as Nike, World Balance, and Adidas are also opening outlet store formats.</div>\r\n<div class=\"_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa\">Gilligan’s, Hap Chan, Choobi-Choobi, Ala Fiesta, Ichiban Boshi, Café De Lipa, LKY Kitchen, and Taza Mia will open 2nd half of this year.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div class=\"_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa\">The Outlets at Lipa is set to be a world-class shopping destination in the Philippines that will feature global retail brands, positioning this shopping hub as one of AboitizLand’s biggest developments.</div>\r\n<div class=\"_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa\">A 9.3-hectare commercial hub located inside the Lima Technology Center in Lipa-Malvar, Batangas, The Outlets will have up to 30,000 square meters of gross leasable space that can accommodate over 200 local and international brands.</div>', 'Aboitiz Pitch opens, complements brands opening at The Outlets', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', '', '', '', '2018-07-17 03:51:41', '2018-07-17 03:51:41', '', 0, 'http://beta.theloop.ph/theoutletslipa/?post_type=promos_and_events&#038;p=246', 0, 'promos_and_events', '', 0),
(248, 1, '2018-07-17 03:56:51', '2018-07-17 03:56:51', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What if you can live your life never settling for anything less than everything? What if you could squeeze every drop; savor every bite, enjoy every second, groove to every beat, give it your all and get it all back in return?</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This philosophy is at the very heart of The Outlets at Lipa, the 9.3 hectare commercial, lifestyle and leisure destination created by AboitizLand Inc., the real estate arm of the Aboitiz Group of Companies.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Whether it be outlet shopping, dining, entertainment, or outdoor activities, The Outlets at Lipa promises to provide the all-out enjoyment every family wants and deserves.</span>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ALL-ACCESS LOCATION</span></i>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Outlets at Lipa is strategically located at the entrance to the LIMA Technolgy Center along the national road of Lipa City. The city itself is the gateway to the Southern Tagalog Region and is easily accessible via an extensive network of highways reaching all the way to Makati in Metro Manila. And of the 2.7 million Batangueños, over 500,000 of them live within 10 kilometers of The Outlets at Lipa.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Batangas province also has one of the Philippines’ fastest growing economies. And its residents are eager reap the rewards of their hard work and get the most out of life – something which they are sure to experience at The Outlets at Lipa.</span>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '31-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-07-17 03:56:51', '2018-07-17 03:56:51', '', 31, 'http://beta.theloop.ph/theoutletslipa/31-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
