(300, 1, '2018-07-19 02:33:47', '2018-07-19 02:33:47', '<div class=\"_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa\">Considered to be the largest artificial turf in Luzon, Aboitiz Pitch opened last June 23 and will complement global and local brands coming to The Outlets at Lipa.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div class=\"_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa\">With a one-day football festival of top Batangas football clubs on its Live All Out event, Aboitiz Pitch launched as an outdoor multi-purpose sports field guaranteeing action-packed activities. It has an open-air layout for a relaxed atmosphere that goes with grand stand and amenities. Various sports can be played including Ultimate Frisbee, Flag football, Dodgeball and Football.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div class=\"_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa\">Complementing the multi-sports field, The Outlets at Lipa will also carry outstanding variety of premium lifestyle brands including H&amp;M, Oakley, Reef, and Dickies, among others, offering discount shopping 365 days of the year.</div>\r\n<div class=\"_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa\">More so, The Outlets will also bring several house of brands such as 158 Designer\'s Boulevard, Bambu, Sunglass Haven, Super Shopbox, Optique Outlet, Sports Warehouse, and US Department Store. Sports brands such as Nike, World Balance, and Adidas are also opening outlet store formats.</div>\r\n<div class=\"_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa\">Gilligan’s, Hap Chan, Choobi-Choobi, Ala Fiesta, Ichiban Boshi, Café De Lipa, LKY Kitchen, and Taza Mia will open 2nd half of this year.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div class=\"_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa\">The Outlets at Lipa is set to be a world-class shopping destination in the Philippines that will feature global retail brands, positioning this shopping hub as one of AboitizLand’s biggest developments.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div class=\"_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa\">A 9.3-hectare commercial hub located inside the Lima Technology Center in Lipa-Malvar, Batangas, The Outlets will have up to 30,000 square meters of gross leasable space that can accommodate over 200 local and international brands.</div>', 'Aboitiz Pitch opens, complements brands opening at The Outlets', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'aboitiz-pitch-opens-complements-brands-opening-at-the-outlets', '', '', '2018-07-19 02:33:47', '2018-07-19 02:33:47', '', 0, 'http://beta.theloop.ph/theoutletslipa/?post_type=promos_and_events&#038;p=300', 0, 'promos_and_events', '', 0),
