(361, 1, '2017-07-06 23:38:42', '2017-07-06 23:38:42', 'The Outlets at Lipa to deliver authentic outlet shopping experience\n\n\n\nArtist’s perspective of The Outlets at Lipa located in Lipa-Malvar Batangas.\n\nIn the time of the internet, social media, and digital advertising, Filipinos are better exposed to information on the latest fashion trends and the biggest brands worldwide. However, despite the existence of variety in the market, discounts may be limited for premium brand items thus the option to refer to seasonal sales. To address this evident need, AboitizLand is set to create The Outlets—a shopping destination that introduces premium brands at reduced price points all year round.\n\nAboitizLand, one of the biggest real-estate developers in the country, offers a complete outlet shopping experience through The Outlets at Lipa, its first commercial venture in Luzon.\n\nCatering to both brand conscious and price conscious shoppers, The Outlets at Lipa will offer a variety of retail outlet stores that meet the needs of discerning shoppers seeking premium items at a discount and customers awaiting seasonal or occasion-led sales for a good purchase. “The Outlets at Lipa is definitely an authentic outlet shopping destination. We offer a 365-day shopping experience, providing easy access to premium brands at discount prices every day of the year. We are looking at around 200 brands, at a location that offers a mix between shopping and dining—there’s retail, there’s food—and some basic utilities to be housed in the area,” says John Amon, AboitizLand’s Vice President and Head of Innovation.\n\nThe Outlets at Lipa offers an authentic retail-lifestyle experience to the Luzon market. “At The Outlets at Lipa, we serve not just the immediate market in the area. We aim to satisfy customers with more than just a great retail deal by including a good mix of food options and exciting outdoor activities. We also have a multi-sports field and beautiful outdoor spaces for families to enjoy. When people actually drive to the place, they can spend an entire day shopping, eating, with the kids playing football, watching live concerts—it’s really designed as a destination worth visiting,” he said.\n\n\n\nArtist’s perspective of the multi-sports field at The Outlets at Lipa.\n\nA 90-minute drive from Manila, the 9.3-hectare property is found within the Lima Technology Center in Lipa-Malvar Batangas. The Outlets at Lipa is set to open during the summer of 2018.', 'Soon to rise: the biggest outlet destination in Luzon', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'soon-to-rise-the-biggest-outlet-destination-in-luzon-2', '', '', '2017-07-06 23:38:42', '2017-07-06 23:38:42', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/theoutletslipa/?post_type=promos_and_events&amp;p=294', 0, 'promos_and_events', '', 0),
(362, 1, '2017-07-10 23:39:38', '2017-07-10 23:39:38', 'Construction update as of Q2 2017. Photos on the progress of the construction site are available to give perspective to all future business partn...', 'Check the landscape and the Construction Progress', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'check-the-landscape-and-the-construction-progress', '', '', '2017-07-10 23:39:38', '2017-07-10 23:39:38', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/theoutletslipa/?post_type=promos_and_events&amp;p=295', 0, 'promos_and_events', '', 0),
(363, 1, '2017-07-10 23:40:59', '2017-07-10 23:40:59', 'When it comes to combining food, fashion, family, and fun, The Outlets at Lipa always has something exciting in mind.\n\nEnvisioned to offer a complete active lifestyle destination, AboitizLand’s commercial development will house top sports brands like Adidas, Planet Sports, The Yard (NBA Store), New Era among others, offering discount shopping 365 days of the year.\n\nMore so, the largest outlet mall in the Philippines is set to host an outdoor multi-purpose sports field. It guarantees action-packed activities with an open-air layout for a relaxed atmosphere.\n\nBringing in outstanding variety of premium brands, The Outlets at Lipa is set to be a world-class shopping destination in the Philippines. It will feature more global retail brands, positioning this shopping hub as one of AboitizLand’s biggest developments.\n\nA 90-minute drive from Manila, the 9.3-hectare property is found within the Lima Technology Center in Lipa-Malvar Batangas. The Outlets at Lipa is set to open during the summer of 2018.', 'Global sports brands join The Outlets at Lipa', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'global-sports-brands-join-the-outlets-at-lipa', '', '', '2017-07-10 23:40:59', '2017-07-10 23:40:59', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/theoutletslipa/?post_type=promos_and_events&amp;p=296', 0, 'promos_and_events', '', 0),
(364, 1, '2017-10-26 23:41:42', '2017-10-26 23:41:42', '<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The outlet mall concept has long been seen to be in a good position for future success.</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With its ability to give consumers better overall value than traditional malls, the concept is considered to be a beneficiary of new shopper dynamics. By redefining their product mix, offering consistent value, and building in more strategic locations, this ensures outlet malls leaping to the next level.</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 500;\">Understanding outlet malls</strong></p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It is important to understand the evolution of the outlet mall as a prelude to where the industry is headed. In the US, outlet malls were built outside major metropolitan areas, relied on tourists as a large customer base, and maintained a markedly different feel from the regional shopping center. These gives consumers a clear choice between two totally different shopping experiences.</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 500;\">Rise of outlet malls in the Philippines</strong></p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In the Philippines, outlet shopping is considered to be a new retailing portal. Exploring the outlet concept can be highly beneficial to retailers in a handful of way due to:</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 500;\"><i><em>Buying Patterns Shift.</em></i></strong>\nMiddle market is now more capable of discretionary spending through fashion, consumer electronics, among others.</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 500;\"><i><em>Multi-Channel strategy</em></i></strong><i><em>.</em></i>\nEstablished brands have taken advantage of diversifying their distribution strategy through keeping inventories fresh in their regular malls and push balance inventories outside the metro.</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 500;\"><i><em>Foreign Brand Influx.</em></i></strong>\nWith the Philippines growing economy, global brands are looking for a bustling market with evolving preferences and shifting buying patterns.</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 500;\"><i><em>Philippines’ Continued Economic Growth.</em></i></strong></p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The significant growth in the private sector, which includes many business operating under retailing, continues to boost the country’s economy. This gives retailers and manufacturers avenues to grow their business as shoppers get more opportunities to buy.</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With the rise of digital marketing and advertising, buyers are better exposed to information on the latest trends in fashion and the latest brands worldwide. Despite the option of variety of premium brands and items in the market, discounts may be limited thus the option to opt for seasonal sales.</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Understanding this evident need, AboitizLand has put up the first outlet shopping destination in Cebu called The Outlets at Pueblo Verde and is now putting up the newest outlet shopping destination in Luzon with The Outlets at Lipa. Bringing in outstanding variety of brands, The Outlets at Lipa is set to be a shopping destination in the country. It will meet the needs of discerning shoppers seeking premium items at a discount and customers awaiting seasonal sales for a good purchase.</p>', 'On the rise: Outlet mall shopping in the Philippines', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'on-the-rise-outlet-mall-shopping-in-the-philippines', '', '', '2017-10-26 23:41:42', '2017-10-26 23:41:42', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/theoutletslipa/?post_type=promos_and_events&amp;p=297', 0, 'promos_and_events', '', 0),
