(367, 1, '2017-10-26 23:47:10', '2017-10-26 23:47:10', '<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Outlets at Lipa is bringing its celebration of fashion directly to shoppers.</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Premium brands such as Levi’s, Giordano, Dickies, NBA Store’s Outlet The Yard and US Department Store will be joining the largest outlet mall destination in Luzon in its opening this 2018. Estimated to draw more than 10 million visitors annually, shoppers will be offered with premium brands in their preferred-style and budget. More brands are expected to join to make sure that the brands are well-represented for fashionistas to millennials, moms and savers.</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Located in Lipa, Batangas, the site can accommodate as much as 27,000 sq.m. for outlet shops. It offers 80sqm. to 600sqm. parcels for anchor stores, restaurants, service businesses and other retail uses.</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Outlets at Lipa  is set to be a world-class shopping destination in the Philippines. It will feature more global retail brands, positioning this shopping hub as one of AboitizLand’s biggest developments.</p>', 'Top apparel brands expand shopping at The Outlets at Lipa', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'top-apparel-brands-expand-shopping-at-the-outlets-at-lipa', '', '', '2017-10-26 23:47:10', '2017-10-26 23:47:10', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/theoutletslipa/?post_type=promos_and_events&amp;p=300', 0, 'promos_and_events', '', 0),
(368, 1, '2017-12-05 23:48:50', '2017-12-05 23:48:50', '<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Want to score great deals and great finds this holiday season? AboitizLand brought in a good combination of food, fashion, family, and fun with The Outlets’ Holiday Wonderfair happening from December 1 to January 6 at The Outlets at Lipa, Lima Technology Center, Lipa, Batangas.</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"></p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Giving a glimpse of its first commercial community in Luzon, The Outlets’ holiday celebration kicked off with a Christmas Tree Lighting on December 1 to welcome shoppers who are up for a whole lot of merrymaking at the heart of Calabarzon.</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lighting the night with an incredible holiday display, everyone was treated to a night of family fun with The Juans at The Outlets Food Market featuring homegrown Batangas brands. The Food Market will run until January 6, 2018.</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"></p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"></p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A Clearance Madness Sale, which will run from December 13 - 17, 2017 featuring a wide range of local and international brands, will let shoppers enjoy an assortment of great finds ensuring the shopping list is something you don’t have to check twice.</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"></p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A 90-minute drive from Manila, The Outlets at Lipa is a 9.3-hectare property found within the Lima Technology Center in Lipa-Malvar, Batangas. Set to open during the summer of 2018, this new outlet shopping destination will feature family-friendly open spaces with wide pathways, alongside an extensive variety of restaurants and food stops.</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"></p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Outlets at Lipa will feature global retail brands, positioning this shopping destination as one of AboitizLand’s biggest commercial development.</p>', 'Getting in the Holiday Wonderfair at The Outlets', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'getting-in-the-holiday-wonderfair-at-the-outlets', '', '', '2017-12-05 23:48:50', '2017-12-05 23:48:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/theoutletslipa/?post_type=promos_and_events&amp;p=302', 0, 'promos_and_events', '', 0),
