(373, 1, '2018-01-11 23:51:03', '2018-01-11 23:51:03', 'AEV President and CEO Erramon Aboitiz together with his team went on a field visit to The Outlets and Lima Technology Center last January 5.\n\nThe site visit started with a brief viewing of The Outlets at Lipa scale model. Together with The Outlets at Lipa team led by Industrial and Commercial Business Unit Head Charity Marohombsar, the team did a walkthrough of the whole development, paving the way to meet and discuss updates and developments of The Outlets at Lipa and Lima Technology Center. It also included an inspection of the facilities within the industrial park.', 'Aboitiz CEO visits The Outlets and Lima Technology Center', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'aboitiz-ceo-visits-the-outlets-and-lima-technology-center', '', '', '2018-01-11 23:51:03', '2018-01-11 23:51:03', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/theoutletslipa/?post_type=promos_and_events&amp;p=305', 0, 'promos_and_events', '', 0),
