(377, 1, '2018-03-13 23:54:02', '2018-03-13 23:54:02', '<div>\n\nThe Outlets at Lipa is complementing shopping and dining with a multi-sports field. Football enthusiasts from inside and outside the city can soon enjoy an action-filled weekend at the football turf as well as the many lifestyle activities offered at The Outlets.\n\n</div>\n<div>\n\nThe field which can be converted to an Olympic-sized football field is at 106x92m, conforming to FIFA and AFC standards. It utilizes Limonta Infinity, one of the high-performing turfs and considered to be the strongest yarn in the market today.\n\n</div>\n<div>\n\nWith 1500-seating capacity, it guarantees action-packed activities in an open-air layout for a relaxed atmosphere. It is also equipped with several sets of locker and shower rooms for the multi-sports field users.\n\n</div>\n<div>\n\nA 9.3-hectare development located inside the Lima Technology Center in Lipa-Malvar, Batangas, The Outlets will have almost 30,000 square meters of gross leasable space that can accommodate over 200 local and international brands.  With construction well underway, The Outlets is set to open in the second quarter of 2018.\n\n</div>', 'Play football at the biggest and strongest artificial football turf in Luzon!', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'play-football-at-the-biggest-and-strongest-artificial-football-turf-in-luzon', '', '', '2018-03-13 23:54:02', '2018-03-13 23:54:02', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/theoutletslipa/?post_type=promos_and_events&amp;p=309', 0, 'promos_and_events', '', 0),
